<h2 class="bold font-l">Race to the Edge-Epilogue</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
A narration from Hiccup describing what happens after the finale battle with the Dragon Hunters </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WhereAreTheyNowEpilogue" class='trope-example-link'>"Where Are They Now?" Epilogue</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="y0je5u" data-video-descrip="The Midnight Sun is an annual two-week long astronomical event where the sun does not set. The perpetual day time is driving the vikings bonkers to varying degrees from a lack of sleep." data-video-title="&quot;The Longest Day&quot;" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/y0je5u_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/y0je5u.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/InsomniaEpisode" data-video-tropename="Insomnia Episode" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Recap/DragonsRidersOfBerkS6E7TheLongestDay,WesternAnimation/DragonsRidersOfBerk" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/y0je5u.jpg">
